## 🗺️ Section 3: Detailed User Flows

### NidhiAI — User Flow (3-Minute Demo)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["👤 NGO Leader opens NidhiAI"] --> B["📤 Uploads documents: 12A cert, 80G cert, NGO description, past impact report"]
    B --> C["🤖 SUPERVISOR receives request"]
    C --> D["⚖️ COMPLIANCE AGENT scans documents via Textract"]
    D --> E{"✅ All docs valid?"}
    E -- "Yes" --> F["🕵️ GRANT SCOUT queries CSR Knowledge Base"]
    E -- "No ❌" --> G["⚠️ Alert: '80G certificate expired. Renew before applying.'"]
    F --> H["📋 Returns top 3 matching CSR opportunities"]
    H --> I["📝 PROPOSAL AGENT writes grant application using RAG"]
    I --> J["📄 Output: Ready-to-send Proposal PDF"]
    J --> K["👤 NGO Leader reviews and sends"]
```

**Demo Timeline (3 mins)**:
- **0:00–0:30**: Show the problem (statistics, emotional hook)
- **0:30–1:00**: NGO leader uploads docs → compliance check runs (green/red indicators)
- **1:00–1:30**: Grant Scout finds matching CSR opportunities (show agent trace)
- **1:30–2:30**: Proposal Agent drafts a full proposal (show real output PDF)
- **2:30–3:00**: Summary + impact potential + future vision

### FreelanceForce — User Flow (3-Minute Demo)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["👤 Student opens FreelanceForce"] --> B["📋 Uploads portfolio: GitHub, resume, skills list"]
    B --> C["🤖 SUPERVISOR receives request"]
    C --> D["🕵️ GIG SCOUT searches mocked job listings"]
    D --> E["📋 Returns 5 matching gigs with match scores"]
    E --> F["Student selects a gig to apply for"]
    F --> G["✍️ PROPOSAL AGENT drafts personalized pitch"]
    G --> H["📄 Output: Ready-to-send proposal"]
    H --> I["👤 Student reviews, edits, sends"]
```

